- Benissimo.

278
00:18:35,760 --> 00:18:39,200
[IL PUBBLICO ACCLAMA]

279
00:18:55,600 --> 00:18:58,400
# Un puntino in mezzo all’universo

280
00:18:58,440 --> 00:19:01,680
# Ero un alieno mi sentivo solo

281
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:04,600
# Mi confondevo tra la gente perso

282
00:19:04,640 --> 00:19:08,200
