354
00:24:04,240 --> 00:24:05,600
Esatto.

355
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:08,760
- Viene quasi naturale.
- Veramente.

356
00:24:08,800 --> 00:24:10,360
"Resta con me."

357
00:24:10,400 --> 00:24:14,040
