Anema e core. #

924
01:02:42,760 --> 01:02:46,880
- Benvenuta.
[IL PUBBLICO ACCLAMA]

925
01:02:46,920 --> 01:02:49,560
Lo struggente e commovente racconto

926
01:02:49,600 --> 01:02:52,560
